{"tid":898373,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「在哪裡呢？」GFRIEND Yuju缺席11月全部行程！公司不解釋引發粉絲擔憂","createTime":"2018-11-11T15:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T07:45:28.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"eb3565f34949ee3ca04fdd5576e7d7933805a72e","tid":898373,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_4b2b52682269a3e00e583bec2f835649/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-08/111027-674305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_4b2b52682269a3e00e583bec2f835649%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-08%2F111027-674305.jpg&h=37f9821e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從10月27日的行程之後，見不到Yuju參與行程，甚至在GFRIEND的11月公開行程裡，Yuju都將缺席。 11月行程表上所有演出活動都標注了（우주 불참），也就是「Yuju缺席」的意思。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_136ef669ea3e3b2136ab6e7b57995101/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-08/111027-674311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_136ef669ea3e3b2136ab6e7b57995101%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-08%2F111027-674311.jpg&h=626ae5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然Yuju和《月刊尹鐘信》合作的歌曲在9日公開，但這也是之前已經完成的行程。而且GFRIEND所屬公司沒有對於Yuju缺席的原因作出回應，這種情況加深了粉絲的憂慮。 紛紛在Twitter用 #WhereIsYuju 請求公司回應、表示思念擔憂等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4c6a42e9c4919b431c2913a36e09b144/static.koreastardaily.com/2018-11-08/111027-674302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4c6a42e9c4919b431c2913a36e09b144%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2018-11-08%2F111027-674302.jpg&h=edd6a004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好彩我轉左去做WIZONCE<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3955eeec5e0776bfb44c07939f080e45174d7261","tid":898373,"uid":177955,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"cite